[normal]conceived 
[normal]for 
[normal]the 
[normal]car
[normal]’
[normal]s 
[normal]convenience whilst moving 
[normal]is most unlikely ever to be convenient or desirable for cycling whereas the ‘traditional city’ London in large part for instance, is connected and with a ch
[normal]oice of destination on offer and where the bike is frequently the most convenient and quickest travel mode
