[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]The consequence of the ubiquity of DMRB in practice is that thinking about users and facilities is ‘controlled’, to some significant extent, by concern over vehicular speed, volume and avoiding congestion of motor 
[normal]traffic.  In comparison the German Roads Guidance, RASt06 (which I translated into English
