[normal]gh. 
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]A County defence that an expensive and poorly located Toucan crossing ‘has to remain, or DfT would withdraw funding’, is spurious.  
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]It is irresponsible to spend money just because its there, it belongs to us all. 
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]Perhaps the money should be given 
[normal]back to DfT/Treasury, or at least leave requested to produce an effective scheme.  In my understanding of the DfT assessor's comments, a rethink was called for anyway.  It is not too late to do something effective; it’s the will that is lacking.
